header: Test vectors of type AeadTest test authenticated encryption with
additional data. The test vectors are intended for testing both

notes.OldVersion: This is a test vector from https://eprint.iacr.org/2013/695.pdf. This paper describes an old version of AEGIS128L. The tag is computed as sum over S[0] .. S[7]. However, the Caesar competition submission http://competitions.cr.yp.to/round1/aegisv1.pdf computes the tag as sum over S[0] .. S[6].
